{"tid":1556926,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"義載BBC記者去機場 港版逆權司機感激報道反送中：港人永不放棄爭取自由 6小時前 即時要聞","createTime":"2019-09-10T02:23:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T02:23:04.000Z","uid":68738,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38f93559ba2466d95d0f98c95619a9405d671ff0","tid":1556926,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059073_417e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059073_417e.jpg&h=06756167&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059205_d1b4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059205_d1b4.png&h=cfb187b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民指義載情景「點解咁有畫面？好似邊套戲咁呢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059205_02d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059205_02d5.jpg&h=2ecce31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n逆權司機叮囑Stephen McDonell：「唔該幫我哋話畀全世界知，香港人永遠唔會放棄！我哋會繼續爭取我哋嘅自由。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059421_2d11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059421_2d11.jpg&h=7d08dcdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMcDonell採訪守護香港集會，遭大媽罵「假新聞」。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190910/large/1568059421_d712.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568059421_d712.jpg&h=31aff114&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMcDonell手持警方發射的催淚彈和橡膠子彈，聲稱面罩被擊毀。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n反送中運動引發全港逾3個月的逆權運動，各行各業從業員均有人參與其中，當中除了較廣為人知的醫護界、航空界，原來連一向保守、被視為要「為口奔馳」的的士司機都支持。事緣BBC駐華記者Stephen McDonell昨天在港（9日）乘坐飛機航班離開，在搭的士去機場、到達客運大樓時，司機表示很感激國際媒體在這幾個月對反送中運動的報道，司機不僅堅持沒有收McDonell車錢，更握着McDonell的手，並叮囑他：「唔該幫我哋話畀全世界知，香港人永遠唔會放棄！我哋會繼續爭取我哋嘅自由。」<br />\n<br />\n網民隨即轉載Stephen McDonell相關tweet，並指「點解咁有畫面？好似邊套戲咁呢？香港幾時變到咁㗎？」不禁令人想起2017年上映的韓國電影《逆權司機》。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190910/60027944?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027944%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=41de99a2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F60027944%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dextra_link&h=ab48ec70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190910/60027944?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=extra_link</a>"}]}